com.hazelcast.map.impl.querycache.publisher

Class QueryCacheListenerRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.map.impl.querycache.publisher.QueryCacheListenerRegistry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Registry<String,String>

    public class QueryCacheListenerRegistry
extends Object
implements Registry<String,String>
    Holds IDs of registered listeners which are registered to listen underlying IMap events to feed QueryCache.

    This class contains mappings like: cacheId ---> registered listener IDs for underlying IMap.
